# Deployment Rules

## Environment
- Node 20+
- npm (not yarn or pnpm)
- Port 3000 for development

## Commands
- `npm install` — install dependencies
- `npm run dev` — start dev server
- `npm run build` — production build
- `npm start` — start production server

## Preview Deploy
- Vercel is the target platform
- Every PR should be deployable
- No build warnings allowed
